html_validator_tool
===================

->Api call will be sent through the net/http calls
->W3C validator has used as a API through rails app.


Setup
=====
1) bundle install.
2) rake asset:precompile
3) rake db:create


App configuration
=================
Ruby - 1.9.3
Rails - 3.1.0

Deployment
==========
Heroku

Version management tool
========================
Git
